> EVAL ``unity_mod (ZN 5) 3 [2; 0; 0; 0; 0; 0; 0; 1]``; --> [2; 1; 0]
> EVAL ``unity_mod_special (ZN 5) 3 7 2``; --> [2; 1; 0]  yes  x + 2
