            = (poly_sum (GENLIST (\k. (q ' k * p * X ** k) % z) (SUC (deg q)))) % z
   Let f3 = \k. (q ' k * p * X ** k) % z
   The result follows if f2 = f3. By FUN_EQ_THM, this is to show:
       !k'. chop (q ' k' o turn_exp p k') = (q ' k' * p * X ** k') % z

